535
00:35:21,995 --> 00:35:22,829
karena aku.

536
00:35:31,212 --> 00:35:32,047
Tidak juga.

537
00:35:33,798 --> 00:35:34,632
Bagus.

538
00:35:41,890 --> 00:35:45,060
