596
00:41:17,517 --> 00:41:18,768
Sial.

597
00:41:31,030 --> 00:41:32,156
Tak akan ketahuan.

598
00:41:34,701 --> 00:41:35,535
Tak akan.

599
00:41:37,412 --> 00:41:38,788
- Tak akan?
- Tak akan.

600
00:41:38,871 --> 00:41:40,623
- Sungguh?
- Kurasa ini...

601
00:41:42,333 --> 00:41:43,710
kasus perdagangan seks.

602
00:41:45,628 --> 00:41:48,381
Mungkin lebih besar dari dugaan kita.

603
00:41:48,464 --> 00:41:51,676
Dengan bos besar,
seperti kejahatan terorganisir.

604
00:41:53,761 --> 00:41:56,472
Oke. Kalau begitu, ayo lakukan ini.

605
00:41:56,556 --> 00:41:59,225
Ini kasus...

606
00:41:59,684 --> 00:42:00,935
