607
00:42:01,018 --> 00:42:03,020
Ini bukan kasus perdagangan seks.

608
00:42:03,813 --> 00:42:05,189
Ini kasus penganiayaan.

609
00:42:06,149 --> 00:42:07,608
Pak Lee adalah korban.

610
00:42:07,900 --> 00:42:09,902
Ponselnya ada kata sandi, bukan?

611
00:42:10,403 --> 00:42:11,237
Ya.

612
00:42:14,824 --> 00:42:16,701
- Kita aman.
- Jika diretas?

613
00:42:17,160 --> 00:42:18,911
Bolehkah polisi...

614
00:42:19,912 --> 00:42:22,707
memecahkan kata sandinya
dan meretas ponselnya?

615
00:42:24,959 --> 00:42:26,085
Itu ponsel korban.

616
00:42:26,878 --> 00:42:28,629
